project_descr: PAL/ Emergency Humanitarian Aid- Upgrading of WATER Supply and distribution System in Rural Areas of the West Bank ( CAP II )

outputs.output_descr: This project will provide reliable water supply to six Palestinian communities in the West Bank (Ein Qinya, Kufr Qalil, Yatta, Rantis, Shuqba and Baqa Sharqiya) and increase the availability of good quality water to those communities. It will develop water infrastructure projects, including construction, rehabilitation, and installation of house water connection.

project_title: pal/ emergency humanitarian aid- water - cap ii
